title: Video: Watch Joe Biden’s complete appearance on Stephen Colbert’s show
text:
Vice President Joe Biden’s appearance Thursday night on Stephen Colbert’s “Late Show” was the talk of cable news Friday morning. Council on Foreign Relations President Richard Haass, appearing on MSNBC’s “Morning Joe,” characterized BIden’s demeanor as not just authentic, a key word in the current discourse on presidential politics, but “raw.”
